## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="ffc5d-103"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Drawing> 物件是輕量級物件，可讓您將應用程式中加入幾何形狀、 影像、 文字與媒體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ffc5d-103"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Drawing> objects are light-weight objects that enable you to add geometric shapes, images, text, and media to an application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ffc5d-104"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Drawing> 物件會被視為輕量級，因為它們不提供支援[配置](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/layout.md)，[輸入概觀](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/input-overview.md)，和焦點。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ffc5d-104"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Drawing> objects are considered light-weight because they do not provide support for [Layout](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/layout.md), [Input Overview](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/input-overview.md), and focus.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ffc5d-105">因為其效能優勢，繪圖十分適用於背景或美工圖案。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ffc5d-105">Because of their performance benefits, drawings are ideal for backgrounds and clip art.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ffc5d-106">在設計程式時也使用繪圖<xref:System.Windows.Media.Visual>層級。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ffc5d-106">You also use drawings when programming at the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Visual> level.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ffc5d-107">因為它們是繼承自<xref:System.Windows.Freezable>類別<xref:System.Windows.Media.Drawing>物件提供額外的功能，使它們分別適合用來描述美工圖案和背景： 可以宣告為共用多個物件，變成唯讀的並進行安全執行緒。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ffc5d-107">Because they inherit from the <xref:System.Windows.Freezable> class, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Drawing> objects  provide additional features that make them useful for describing clip art and backgrounds: they can be declared as , shared among multiple objects, made read-only, and made thread-safe.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ffc5d-108">如需有關所提供的不同功能<xref:System.Windows.Freezable>物件，請參閱[Freezable 物件概觀](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/freezable-objects-overview.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ffc5d-108">For more information about the different features provided by <xref:System.Windows.Freezable> objects, see the [Freezable Objects Overview](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/freezable-objects-overview.md).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ffc5d-109">有不同類型的<xref:System.Windows.Media.Drawing>不同類型的內容物件： <xref:System.Windows.Media.GeometryDrawing>， <xref:System.Windows.Media.ImageDrawing>， <xref:System.Windows.Media.DrawingGroup>， <xref:System.Windows.Media.VideoDrawing>，和<xref:System.Windows.Media.GlyphRunDrawing>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ffc5d-109">There are different types of <xref:System.Windows.Media.Drawing> objects for different types of content: <xref:System.Windows.Media.GeometryDrawing>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.ImageDrawing>,  <xref:System.Windows.Media.DrawingGroup>,  <xref:System.Windows.Media.VideoDrawing>, and  <xref:System.Windows.Media.GlyphRunDrawing>.</span></span>  
  
